<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contact — Bert Liu</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Get in touch with Bert Liu about Taiwan manufacturing, supplier coordination, and production decisions for hardware teams."
    />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://bertliu.com/contact" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Bert Liu" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Contact — Bert Liu" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="Get in touch with Bert Liu about Taiwan manufacturing, supplier coordination, and production decisions for hardware teams."
    />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://bertliu.com/contact" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://bertliu.com/og-image.jpg" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Contact — Bert Liu" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="Get in touch with Bert Liu about Taiwan manufacturing, supplier coordination, and production decisions for hardware teams."
    />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://bertliu.com/og-image.jpg" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f7f4ed;
        --text: #1f1f1b;
        --muted: #4e4a42;
        --line: #d8d2c5;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        overflow-y: scroll;
        scrollbar-gutter: stable;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background: var(--bg);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      nav,
      .intro-links {
        font-family:
          ui-sans-serif,
          system-ui,
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
      }

      .page {
        width: min(1100px, 100%);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 24px 80px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 220px minmax(0, 1fr);
        column-gap: 56px;
      }

      nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: 48px;
        align-self: start;
        width: 180px;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      nav a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
      }

      nav a:hover,
      nav a:focus-visible {
        color: var(--text);
        border-bottom-color: var(--line);
      }

      nav a[aria-current="page"] {
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 600;
        border-bottom-color: var(--line);
      }

      main {
        grid-column: 2;
        max-width: 750px;
      }

      .intro {
        padding: 0 0 28px;
      }

      .intro-head {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin: 0 0 4px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 2.4rem);
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        line-height: 1.05em;
      }

      .intro-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .intro-links a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
        padding-bottom: 1px;
      }

      .intro-links a:hover,
      .intro-links a:focus-visible {
        color: var(--text);
        border-bottom-color: var(--line);
      }


      p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .intro p {
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 70ch;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

      section {
        padding: 36px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 1.45rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      .contact p {
        max-width: 60ch;
      }

      .contact a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding-bottom: 1px;
      }

      .contact a:hover,
      .contact a:focus-visible {
        border-bottom-color: var(--text);
      }

      .contact-email {
        margin-top: 14px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .contact-links {
  margin-top: 22px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.contact-links a {
  color: var(--text);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding-bottom: 1px;
  width: fit-content;
}

.contact-links a:hover,
.contact-links a:focus-visible {
  border-bottom-color: var(--text);
}

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .page {
          display: block;
          padding: 20px 20px 56px;
        }

        nav {
          position: static;
          width: auto;
          margin-bottom: 24px;
          border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
          padding-bottom: 12px;
        }

        nav ul {
          flex-direction: row;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          gap: 10px 18px;
        }

        .intro-head {
          align-items: flex-end;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        section {
          padding: 28px 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Field Notes</a></li>
          <li><a href="/manufacturing-stack">Manufacturing Stack</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" aria-current="page">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <main>
        <header class="intro">
          <div class="intro-head">
            <h1>Bert Liu</h1>
            <div class="intro-links" aria-label="Social links">
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bertmfg"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="LinkedIn">in</a
              >
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/bertbuilds/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="Instagram">ig</a
              >
              <a href="mailto:bert@bertliu.com" aria-label="Email">✉</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Manufacturing in Taiwan. Notes on factories, systems, and supply chains.
          </p>
        </header>

        <section class="contact">

          <h2>Connect</h2>
        
          <p>
        
            If you’re working through manufacturing or supply-chain decisions — what to keep in-house, what to hand to trusted partners, and where quality needs tighter control — feel free to reach out.
        
          </p>
        
          <div class="contact-links" aria-label="Contact links">
            <a href="mailto:bert@bertliu.com">
              Email — bert@bertliu.com
            </a>
          
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bert-liu-8b3a2323/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              LinkedIn — Bert Liu
            </a>
          
            <a
              href="https://www.instagram.com/bertbuilds/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              Instagram — @bertbuilds
            </a>
          </div>
        
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
